data.description: This beautifully remodeled spacious rambler is sparkling clean and ready for you to call it "home". You're close to all the cafes, restaurants, shops and farmer's market that make West Seattle such a great place to live.  Home features a recently updated kitchen with slab granite and stainless appliances. Lower level is completely finished with full bath, BR, office area and spacious bedroom. The outside is built for summer dinner parties with large covered patio and mature landscaping all on an oversized lot.
